<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Feb1936"><font color="red">1 February 1936</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I was glad to hear from Mrs Jolas that he had been working steadily before this eye trouble came on, aided by you &hellip; You are indeed to him the most devoted, the most helpful and the most disinterested of friends. </div>
